CyberCron may be freely redistributed via BBSs, InterNet/Usenet, and disk
libraries such as Fred Fish's, as long as the archive is not modified.
Disk magazines and services that charge extra for file transfers may not
distribute CyberCron.

In using CyberCron, you accept the responsibility for any damage or loss of
